BASICS
<!DOCTYPE html> - defining 
<html> - container
<title> - tab name
<header> - top text
<meta> - data about the webpage. Placed in header
    <meta name="description" content="XXXX">
                "keywords" - keywords for searh engine
                "author" - author
                "viewport content="width=device-width, initial scale =N" - page scaling on devices
          charset="UTF-8" - char. encoding 
          http-equiv="refresh" content="N" - refreshing page every N seconds
<body> - body
<br> - new line
<hr> - horizontal line
<iframe src=" "> - insert content from another source (webpage)
<!-- COMMNET -->
HYPERLINKS
<a 
href="the link/file name" - setting the link 
href="mailto:what123@gmail.com" - emailing
target=_self - opening link in the existing tab
target=_blank - opening link in new tab
title="text" - setting text when pointing on a link

>
</a>

IMAGES
<img src="link/file location"> -  Adding images
<img height = "N" width = "N"> - dimensions 
<img alt="description"> - adding description to images

<source src=""> - source element

AUDIO
<audio controls> - adding control bar
<audio autoplay muted loop> - autoplay/start muted/loop

TEXT 
<p> - paragraph
<b> - bold
<i> - italic
<big>/<small> - change text size
<sub>/<sup> - move down or up
<ins> - underline
<del> - cross
<marked> - highlight
<span> - modify text or portion of a text
<div> - modify the surrounded text as a single group

LISTS
<ul> <li> text </li> </ul> - unordered list with elements
<ol type="number/letter"> - ordered list
<dl> - description
    <dt> - term
    <dd> - definition

TABLES
<table> - create table
<tr> - table tow
<th> - table header
<td> - table data
<table bgcolor="color" align="alignemnt" width="N" length="N"> - setting table parameters

STYLE  
<style="color: rgb(N, N, N)"> - rgb color

BUTTONS
<button> - create a button

FORMS
<form action="action_page.php" method="POST"> - create a form
<label for="idname"> - create label with and id
<input type="text" id="idname" name="name" placholder="text" maxlength="N"> - get text input from user related to an id. 
Name attribute carries name of the input data. Placeholder is the deafault text
<input type="reset/submit/password/email/tel/date/number/radio">
<select> <option></option> </select> - list of options to choose from
         
